snippet.textDisplay: Thank you for using your likability to share this message with others! When I was younger with less stability in my jobs while going to school, I was so tempted to buy a cheaper version of name brand makeup because I wanted to have a beautiful collection like those I watched on  YouTube. Looking back I am SOOO glad I didn’t do that. Those horror stories of counterfeit makeup gone bad make my skin itch. On top of that, it made me feel so great about myself when I got to the place that I could buy the real deal! Knowing that I have built a collection of makeup starting with drugstore favorites all the way to high end brands without stooping to counterfeit gives me even more confidence in my level of success and I can continue in exploring my love for makeup without worry about getting my lips glued shut or an eye infection. Thank you again Tati!
